or voltages","Needs external flyback diodes on motor outputs (L298N has no built-in protection)","Servo headers share 5V from Arduino — don't power heavy servos from it, use external 5V"],"datasheet_url":""},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},